WEBVTT

00:13.040 --> 00:14.120
Zhao.

00:14.200 --> 00:16.040
You came home safely.

00:16.120 --> 00:17.480
I'm relieved.

00:19.000 --> 00:22.160
PICTURESQUE

00:25.280 --> 00:26.720
Madam, what a good trick.

00:27.720 --> 00:29.280
As the matron of the family,

00:29.360 --> 00:33.040
it is my duty to worry about
the eldest daughter's marriage.

00:34.840 --> 00:37.480
I will repay this kindness well.

00:38.320 --> 00:39.160
Shou Gu!

00:40.800 --> 00:42.200
-Zhang Ru.
-Shou Gu, you're finally home.

00:42.800 --> 00:44.520
-Listen, it's her!
-All right, Zhang Ru.

00:44.600 --> 00:46.200
Let's go and see Grandma first.

01:17.320 --> 01:20.000
I prepared medicine for the illnesses
that grandmothers always have.

01:20.520 --> 01:21.600
When I'm not around,

01:21.680 --> 01:22.720
just prepare the medicine
according to the symptoms.

01:23.400 --> 01:24.560
All right.

01:26.360 --> 01:27.520
The weather is cold.

01:27.600 --> 01:30.280
Get a thicker quilt for Grandma.

01:30.880 --> 01:33.880
Besides that, smoked mugwort
is good for qi and blood.

01:33.960 --> 01:35.360
You can use it during the day for Grandma.

01:35.440 --> 01:36.920
All right, I'll remember that.

01:37.520 --> 01:40.120
By the way, Uncle Shi Shu

01:40.200 --> 01:42.120
brought Gastrodia and cat's claw
herbs from town.

01:42.200 --> 01:44.280
I heard that
it was good for headaches too.

01:45.400 --> 01:46.600
My father was being considerate.

01:51.840 --> 01:53.480
-Grandma.
-Grandma.

01:54.720 --> 01:56.920
Grandma, you're awake.

01:57.520 --> 01:58.440
Shou Gu.

02:00.960 --> 02:02.040
I'm home.

02:02.920 --> 02:04.360
It's good that you're home.

02:05.000 --> 02:06.200
It's all my fault.

02:06.280 --> 02:07.760
I've made you worry about me.

02:08.960 --> 02:10.639
Fortunately, it was nothing serious.

02:10.720 --> 02:12.560
Otherwise, I would never be redeemed
even if I die.

02:19.120 --> 02:21.120
PICTURESQUE

02:21.200 --> 02:22.520
Here, slowly.

02:27.400 --> 02:28.840
I don't blame you.

02:29.520 --> 02:32.800
That malicious woman knew I would
get messed up if I got concerned,

02:32.880 --> 02:34.040
so she exaggerated it.

02:34.640 --> 02:37.760
I got a headache and was confused.

02:37.840 --> 02:42.040
I was afraid that something
might happen to you in Futing.

02:42.120 --> 02:44.000
This hateful Wang Ying Xue.

02:44.080 --> 02:45.720
While Shou Gu went to Futing,

02:45.800 --> 02:46.800
she secretly signed the marriage contract.

02:50.000 --> 02:50.840
Is it the Wei family?

02:54.400 --> 02:56.560
That scoundrel.

02:56.640 --> 02:58.640
I'll get the two scoundrels
to cancel the engagement now!

02:58.720 --> 02:59.760
Grandma.

03:00.920 --> 03:02.160
I'm an adult now.

03:02.240 --> 03:05.040
Let me handle this.

03:05.120 --> 03:07.760
I'll go back to the capital tomorrow
to put an end to this matter.

03:08.360 --> 03:10.040
But you just came home.

03:10.840 --> 03:12.160
Since I can't avoid it,

03:12.760 --> 03:14.360
I should face it bravely.

03:15.400 --> 03:18.080
First of all, it's to solve this matter.

03:18.160 --> 03:19.360
Secondly,

03:19.440 --> 03:22.960
didn't you want me
to see how vast the world is?

03:23.720 --> 03:26.360
I'll broaden my horizons
once I go to the capital.

03:31.600 --> 03:32.520
Shou Gu.

03:33.520 --> 03:36.120
It's all my fault. I'm not in good health.

03:36.760 --> 03:38.160
I can't protect you.

03:38.240 --> 03:40.280
Grandma, please don't say that.

03:41.720 --> 03:42.880
Like you said,

03:43.960 --> 03:46.680
we can't always live
under the protection of others.

03:47.520 --> 03:48.680
So this time,

03:49.240 --> 03:50.960
let me protect you.

03:53.880 --> 03:55.480
With your wisdom,

03:55.560 --> 03:58.000
you can cope with whatever happens.

03:58.720 --> 04:00.040
But remember this.

04:01.040 --> 04:02.200
You must know when to stop.

04:04.520 --> 04:06.600
Old Madam Cui. Look at this.

04:07.720 --> 04:09.280
Alas.

04:10.160 --> 04:12.560
Grandma, when we were young, Shou Gu and I

04:12.640 --> 04:14.200
made Ji'an lotus root dumplings for you.

04:14.280 --> 04:15.160
Do you remember?

04:17.000 --> 04:19.120
Back then, you tried to cook the dumplings

04:19.200 --> 04:21.240
but they blended into a paste instead.

04:22.200 --> 04:26.720
Zhang Ru and I made it for you. Try it.

04:28.280 --> 04:30.440
-Tell us about the taste.
-Try it.

04:32.000 --> 04:32.840
Let's eat.

04:36.720 --> 04:37.800
This time, it's not a paste, right?

04:39.720 --> 04:40.600
Is it tasty?

04:40.680 --> 04:43.320
Yes, it's tasty.

04:45.720 --> 04:46.960
Young Lady Zhao.

04:47.040 --> 04:49.120
These are what ladies in the capital wear.

04:49.200 --> 04:51.880
The Fifth Master said
you should change into this.

04:54.200 --> 04:55.400
I shall take my leave.

04:57.520 --> 05:00.400
He is afraid that you will
go to the capital in plain clothes

05:00.480 --> 05:02.560
and embarrass him.

05:06.080 --> 05:07.880
Grandma's birthday is around the corner.

05:07.960 --> 05:12.040
In previous years, we would listen to
"Plum Blossom By the Ge Stream".

05:12.640 --> 05:14.720
I'm afraid we won't
have the chance this year.

05:22.200 --> 05:23.440
Where does the music come from?

05:40.400 --> 05:43.720
Maybe a passing musician
playing it for fun.

05:57.000 --> 05:58.600
We've listened to the song.

05:59.520 --> 06:02.760
Just treat it as if
you celebrated my birthday.

06:03.480 --> 06:06.760
This song is meant to remind us
not to lose our prime era.

06:07.440 --> 06:08.760
Grandma, you once said that

06:09.840 --> 06:12.240
you're trapped in this house forever.

06:12.320 --> 06:13.960
You haven't been able to
see much of the country.

06:14.640 --> 06:16.800
Once I take care of
the matter in the capital,

06:16.880 --> 06:18.840
let's do what
the lyrics of the song suggest.

06:19.640 --> 06:21.560
We'll take the boat and pick flowers.

06:21.640 --> 06:22.680
We'll travel through
the mountains and rivers.

06:23.520 --> 06:24.480
I'm going too.

06:24.560 --> 06:26.160
You can't leave me behind.

06:27.880 --> 06:30.160
Come on. Grandma, Zhang Ru.

06:30.240 --> 06:31.520
We made a deal.

06:32.160 --> 06:33.120
Wait for my return.

06:34.640 --> 06:36.160
-Come on.
-Sure.

07:58.840 --> 08:02.560
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL "BLOSSOM"
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

08:07.080 --> 08:09.200
CLOUD-LIKE MIND AND CRANE-LIKE EYES

08:22.360 --> 08:23.960
Lord Song, are you not coming out yet?

08:34.880 --> 08:36.760
A man broke into your house in the dark.

08:38.520 --> 08:39.799
Why are you not afraid?

08:39.880 --> 08:42.520
I know it's you, so I'm not afraid.

08:49.960 --> 08:51.400
Thanks for the song.

08:52.080 --> 08:54.120
And thank you for taking care of me
along the way.

08:56.680 --> 08:58.400
I wanted to hide in the dark

08:59.240 --> 09:00.280
and didn't want to disturb you.

09:02.440 --> 09:04.200
You took my advice.

09:04.280 --> 09:05.600
I'm surprised.

09:06.280 --> 09:07.480
Well, it's rare to find a woman

09:07.560 --> 09:08.960
with such an understanding
of the situation.

09:09.040 --> 09:10.520
You're…

09:13.400 --> 09:15.760
the most sophisticated woman
I've ever seen.

09:20.440 --> 09:22.440
I'm not as sophisticated as you think.

09:23.320 --> 09:24.840
I'm troubled by trivial matters at home.

09:26.320 --> 09:28.440
But I don't have
the courage to be decisive.

09:29.560 --> 09:32.160
You can say that I'm good
at helping others but not myself.

09:33.640 --> 09:34.480
Which is why

09:35.120 --> 09:36.920
I decided to learn from you,
to be vigorous and determined.

09:37.960 --> 09:40.120
I'm returning to the capital
to take care of family matters.

09:40.760 --> 09:43.360
Rather than being controlled by others,
it's better to strike first.

09:43.440 --> 09:44.640
All right.

09:44.720 --> 09:47.640
I wish you success all the way.

09:47.720 --> 09:48.800
Thank you.

09:50.880 --> 09:51.760
Lord Song, you didn't come here

09:51.840 --> 09:54.800
just to compliment me, did you?

09:56.240 --> 09:57.440
I came to bid you farewell.

09:58.360 --> 10:00.160
I am leaving for Liaodong later.

10:00.240 --> 10:02.240
I'm afraid I won't be back for a while.

10:02.320 --> 10:03.400
Before leaving,

10:04.800 --> 10:05.840
I'm returning this to you.

10:26.560 --> 10:27.680
If you need help,

10:28.800 --> 10:30.480
just send someone to look for me.

10:33.680 --> 10:35.160
I appreciate your kindness.

10:36.120 --> 10:38.640
But I want to solve it myself.

10:43.480 --> 10:44.360
What flower is this?

10:44.920 --> 10:46.360
You treasure it.

10:47.280 --> 10:48.400
It's Nine-Layered Purple.

10:48.480 --> 10:49.440
Just some wild flowers.

10:56.520 --> 10:58.280
Don't bother.

10:58.880 --> 11:00.600
It can withstand heavy blows.

11:00.680 --> 11:01.680
It grows well on its own.

11:02.840 --> 11:04.760
I believe it will grow well on its own.

11:04.840 --> 11:06.240
But I also believe that

11:07.000 --> 11:09.760
help will make it grow well faster.

11:16.280 --> 11:18.080
DUKE OF YING'S RESIDENCE

11:20.880 --> 11:22.240
So this is chess.

11:23.040 --> 11:24.240
I learned something today, sir.

11:26.680 --> 11:28.040
-Look at this.
-So this step…

11:33.960 --> 11:37.000
Why suddenly there are
many new attendants?

11:37.600 --> 11:39.120
They said there were
many things to handle,

11:39.200 --> 11:40.480
so new people were coming in.

11:40.560 --> 11:41.400
Where is Lu Zheng?

11:41.480 --> 11:44.400
I think the Duke assigned him an errand.
I haven't seen him for days.

11:50.320 --> 11:51.600
-Keep it.
-Let's keep it.

11:51.680 --> 11:52.800
All right.

11:57.240 --> 11:59.520
The Duchess is seriously ill
and has a poor appetite.

11:59.600 --> 12:01.800
Serving her this greasy food
will make her vomit blood.

12:01.880 --> 12:03.120
Are you looking to die?

12:03.200 --> 12:05.040
I was assigned to serve the Duchess today.

12:05.600 --> 12:06.840
I don't know what she likes or dislikes.

12:15.680 --> 12:17.840
How's the Duchess's condition?

12:21.200 --> 12:22.520
The Duchess said
the new medicine is bitter.

12:22.600 --> 12:25.680
The staff in the kitchen are busy
making her favorite preserves.

12:42.680 --> 12:44.160
She was willing to admit
her mistake and return to the capital.

12:44.240 --> 12:46.320
I guess she must have
something up her sleeve.

12:46.400 --> 12:48.160
Madam, you must be careful.

12:50.920 --> 12:52.320
Shou Gu, you're staying here.

12:52.400 --> 12:54.600
Why didn't you tell us in advance?

12:54.680 --> 12:57.000
I could have told them
to make preparations.

12:57.080 --> 12:59.600
I thought you two
discussed this in advance.

13:00.280 --> 13:01.160
The wedding day is drawing near.

13:01.840 --> 13:03.520
I should come back
to prepare for the wedding.

13:04.200 --> 13:06.840
Besides, you found this good match for me.

13:08.200 --> 13:09.520
This is also what Uncle Shi Shu wants.

13:09.600 --> 13:10.840
We're a family.

13:10.920 --> 13:12.160
You should have returned home earlier.

13:12.240 --> 13:14.120
It's good, as Shou Gu has figured it out.

13:14.200 --> 13:15.320
That's right.

13:15.400 --> 13:17.400
But let me be frank.

13:17.480 --> 13:19.920
Shou Gu has not been
staying here for a long time.

13:20.000 --> 13:22.360
I guess she won't be able to adapt to it.

13:23.080 --> 13:24.760
She'll get used to it. It's all right.

13:26.240 --> 13:27.760
Don't stand here.

13:27.840 --> 13:28.920
Let's go inside.

13:29.480 --> 13:30.480
-Gao Sheng!
-Sir.

13:30.560 --> 13:32.480
-Tell them to serve the food now.
-Yes.

13:33.640 --> 13:35.480
Come on, bring the stuff in.

13:36.800 --> 13:38.240
Madam, you're the kindest.

13:38.320 --> 13:41.360
If even you think I am a liability,

13:42.200 --> 13:44.280
then I have no way to go.

13:48.160 --> 13:49.720
Now that you've returned home,

13:49.800 --> 13:52.000
you should follow the rules at home.

13:52.880 --> 13:55.560
You've become wild
after spending years on the farm.

13:55.640 --> 13:57.080
It's time to restrain yourself.

13:58.160 --> 14:00.080
I was stubborn and
mischievous before this.

14:00.160 --> 14:01.600
I've come to my senses.

14:02.240 --> 14:05.280
From now on, I will follow your teaching.

14:07.520 --> 14:09.040
If that's the case,

14:09.120 --> 14:10.920
let's start by copying "Women's Precepts".

14:16.920 --> 14:19.200
Wang Ying Xue is such a vicious woman.

14:19.280 --> 14:20.480
Young Lady Zhao just came back.

14:21.120 --> 14:22.520
But Wang punished her
to copy "Women's Precepts".

14:22.600 --> 14:23.600
Ten times!

14:23.680 --> 14:26.040
We had freedom in Zhengding Farm.

14:26.120 --> 14:27.560
Why did we come here to suffer?

14:28.280 --> 14:29.680
Young Lady Zhao hasn't said anything,

14:29.760 --> 14:30.960
but you have complained a lot.

14:31.560 --> 14:32.760
You like the farm so much.

14:32.840 --> 14:35.160
I'll send you back to the farm tomorrow
to serve Old Madam Cui.

14:35.240 --> 14:37.440
No! I'll keep quiet then.

14:39.400 --> 14:40.240
Who is it?

14:40.320 --> 14:42.320
Young Lady Zhao, Mr. Zhao of the bookstore

14:42.400 --> 14:44.560
told me to deliver the new paper
and inkstone for you.

14:48.680 --> 14:49.720
Mr. Zhao also said that

14:49.800 --> 14:52.600
Ms. Zhao should
read the contents carefully.

15:09.840 --> 15:11.800
DUCHESS JIANG ILL; SERVANTS REPLACED
MR. SONG'S ATTENDANTS MISSING

15:11.880 --> 15:13.200
It's news from Mr. Chen.

15:16.240 --> 15:18.760
All this while, the servants in the
Duke's residence are all the Duke's men.

15:19.360 --> 15:21.360
Why is it that
when the Duchess is seriously ill,

15:21.440 --> 15:23.400
a large number of servants
in the residence were replaced?

15:24.240 --> 15:26.480
"The silver sword cuts straight
into the blue sky."

15:26.560 --> 15:28.400
"I was cast aside
when my purpose was served."

15:29.240 --> 15:31.000
"All the merits done were in vain."

15:32.040 --> 15:34.440
"And the revenge causes internal strife."

15:35.120 --> 15:37.680
Song Mo is going to kill
his father and brother this year.

15:38.360 --> 15:41.320
There's been a strange turn of events
at the Duke of Ying's residence.

15:42.280 --> 15:45.680
Could it be that except
for the death of the Duke of Ding,

15:45.760 --> 15:48.000
there are other reasons
why his behavior changed drastically?

15:48.080 --> 15:50.440
I need to tell Mr. Chen to check it.

15:51.280 --> 15:52.240
Who's there?

15:52.840 --> 15:54.280
Zhao, it's me.

16:02.640 --> 16:04.240
This is steamed sea bass.

16:04.320 --> 16:06.120
This is ham and bamboo shoot soup.

16:06.200 --> 16:09.080
During the family dinner,
I saw you had a few more bites.

16:09.160 --> 16:10.000
You probably like it.

16:13.160 --> 16:14.760
I made it.

16:23.240 --> 16:24.280
It's tasty.

16:29.280 --> 16:30.120
Let's eat together.

16:38.440 --> 16:40.440
Your mother grounded me and
punished me to copy "Women's Precepts".

16:40.520 --> 16:41.520
No one is allowed to visit me.

16:41.600 --> 16:44.120
Aren't you afraid of being punished
by coming here?

16:46.200 --> 16:47.360
Blame me for being incompetent.

16:48.200 --> 16:50.000
My mother is dissatisfied with me.

16:51.000 --> 16:52.840
That's why she is wary of you.

16:52.920 --> 16:54.120
She's afraid that Father would be biased.

16:59.480 --> 17:02.360
I copied some of
the "Women's Precepts" for you.

17:02.960 --> 17:04.400
I brought some books too.

17:05.000 --> 17:06.760
There are novels and songbooks.

17:06.839 --> 17:08.200
Maybe it can relieve your boredom.

17:08.280 --> 17:10.119
It's your first time here.

17:10.200 --> 17:13.200
I know the most popular shops for rouge,

17:13.280 --> 17:16.319
fabrics, and stationery in the town.

17:17.720 --> 17:19.599
We can also rent a boat.

17:19.680 --> 17:21.440
At that time,

17:21.520 --> 17:23.520
we'll take a boat ride
and listen to songs.

17:25.359 --> 17:27.000
That was before I was born.

17:27.079 --> 17:29.320
But I've heard elders mention it.

17:29.400 --> 17:30.720
I didn't know much.

17:31.320 --> 17:32.560
Once you regain your freedom,

17:32.640 --> 17:34.160
I'll go with you.

17:38.680 --> 17:42.600
Zhao, you don't want to
take a boat ride, do you?

17:43.600 --> 17:44.520
That's not it.

17:45.880 --> 17:50.840
It's just that the old you
and the present you

17:50.920 --> 17:52.040
are simply different.

17:54.040 --> 17:55.440
The old me?

18:02.880 --> 18:03.720
Someone's here.

18:04.960 --> 18:06.160
Hurry!

18:12.600 --> 18:14.200
Let's stop here.

18:16.400 --> 18:17.960
I'm tired. I need to rest.

18:41.800 --> 18:43.160
He's left.

18:43.240 --> 18:44.200
He's left.

19:01.920 --> 19:03.440
I should take my leave then.

19:04.160 --> 19:05.280
Goodbye.

19:11.520 --> 19:14.440
This is weird. How did they know
you were punished?

19:15.800 --> 19:17.560
This is Ming's.

19:17.640 --> 19:19.640
She thought of it too.

19:19.720 --> 19:20.760
She's thoughtful.

19:25.760 --> 19:27.320
Ming's handwriting…

19:27.400 --> 19:29.280
Wang Ying Xue
will definitely recognize it.

19:29.920 --> 19:31.320
It's better not to trouble her.

19:32.000 --> 19:33.160
I appreciate her thought.

19:34.560 --> 19:35.800
This is from Mr. Wu.

19:36.560 --> 19:37.400
Can we use it?

19:37.480 --> 19:38.720
WOMEN'S PRECEPTS

19:40.440 --> 19:42.120
His handwriting is clear and straight,

19:42.200 --> 19:44.560
while the return of
the brush's tip is tactful.

19:46.800 --> 19:49.520
But no matter how you look at it,
it looks like a man's handwriting.

19:50.240 --> 19:51.560
You can see that,

19:51.640 --> 19:53.320
but Wang Ying Xue
may not see that.

19:53.400 --> 19:55.360
She won't check it in such detail.

19:57.560 --> 20:00.120
Why is Mr. Ji's handwriting so crooked?

20:00.200 --> 20:01.600
WOMEN'S PRECEPTS

20:02.560 --> 20:04.000
Jian Ming knows I write
hiding the brush's tip.

20:04.080 --> 20:05.400
He knows I write letters

20:05.480 --> 20:07.520
with my left hand instead.

20:08.240 --> 20:09.800
It's quite a good imitation.

20:09.880 --> 20:11.680
That means we can use it, right?

20:13.200 --> 20:14.680
Here's another one from Lord Song.

20:14.760 --> 20:16.400
His handwriting looks crooked too.

20:18.720 --> 20:20.640
I OWE MY GUIDANCE
TO MY MOTHER AND TEACHERS…

20:26.000 --> 20:28.360
No, he got this character wrong.

20:28.440 --> 20:31.360
Look at the character "qiu".

20:31.440 --> 20:33.080
There was a missing dot in it.

20:34.720 --> 20:37.400
QIU

20:38.160 --> 20:40.120
My lady, is there anything wrong?

20:41.040 --> 20:43.680
This handwriting is exactly the same
as what I write with my left hand.

20:45.240 --> 20:46.760
To avoid writing
my deceased mother's name,

20:47.880 --> 20:51.000
I remove the dot when I write "qiu".

20:51.760 --> 20:53.520
Lord Song is such a good observer.

20:54.240 --> 20:56.360
Does that mean we can use both of these?

20:56.440 --> 20:58.240
There's no conclusion to this.

20:58.320 --> 20:59.640
I say we should use both.

21:06.400 --> 21:08.200
ORCHID AND ANGELICA FOREVER FLOURISHING

21:14.080 --> 21:16.160
LIAODONG

21:38.560 --> 21:40.440
The Jiangs are a family of heroes.

21:40.520 --> 21:42.040
I've always admired them.

21:43.400 --> 21:45.440
It's just that the imperial edict
has just been issued.

21:45.520 --> 21:48.880
If they're given preferential treatment,
I'm afraid he'll be impeached again.

21:48.960 --> 21:50.320
ZHU YOU TING, PRINCE QING

21:50.400 --> 21:51.720
What do you think, Mr. Ji?

21:54.040 --> 21:55.320
Lord Song is brave.

21:55.400 --> 21:56.360
Your Highness cherishes his talents.

21:57.320 --> 21:59.320
If Lord Song can be of
any help to Your Highness,

21:59.400 --> 22:01.080
it's a win-win situation.

22:01.160 --> 22:02.320
Wouldn't it be better?

22:03.080 --> 22:04.120
Lizhen frequently harassed us.

22:04.200 --> 22:06.200
His Highness has been busy
preparing for war.

22:06.960 --> 22:09.080
Lord Song is a good-looking general
who became famous at a young age.

22:09.760 --> 22:11.080
He must be highly skilled.

22:13.800 --> 22:15.400
Lizhen grew up on horses.

22:15.480 --> 22:18.680
They must be cavalries.

22:19.440 --> 22:22.360
They're not these motionless straw men.

22:50.560 --> 22:51.600
Twenty feet.

22:53.640 --> 22:54.680
Great!

22:54.760 --> 22:57.120
There are brocade clouds in the sky.
This is an auspicious omen.

22:57.200 --> 23:00.480
It seems that the
Star of the General is here.

23:00.560 --> 23:01.640
It's good enough to protect the border.

23:06.640 --> 23:09.320
Lord Song, your reputation precedes you.
It's indeed true.

23:10.520 --> 23:11.720
-Shi Chuan.
-Yes.

23:12.320 --> 23:14.440
Send some men to repair
the houses of the Jiangs.

23:15.080 --> 23:16.040
Take the medical officer with you.

23:16.120 --> 23:16.960
Yes.

23:19.680 --> 23:21.480
Yan Tang, why don't you stay here with me?

23:21.560 --> 23:22.720
Train my army for me.

23:22.800 --> 23:24.920
You can also take care of the Jiangs.

23:25.000 --> 23:27.240
I can ask my father for a decree.

23:28.320 --> 23:29.240
Thank you for your kindness,
Your Highness.

23:29.880 --> 23:31.920
But I just received
an urgent report from the capital.

23:32.000 --> 23:34.280
Mother is getting seriously ill.
I'm afraid…

23:34.360 --> 23:35.920
Report!

23:36.880 --> 23:38.160
Your Highness! Lizhen attacked again.

23:38.760 --> 23:40.000
There are ten times the normal troops.

23:40.080 --> 23:42.320
I'm afraid it's more than harassment.

23:42.400 --> 23:44.680
Send orders to various teams.
Get all the soldiers and horses ready

23:44.760 --> 23:45.880
and go to war with me!

23:46.640 --> 23:48.920
Send the emergency report
to the imperial court!

23:49.000 --> 23:51.000
-Yes!
-I'm about to return to the capital.

23:51.080 --> 23:52.000
I'll deliver the emergency report.

23:56.240 --> 23:57.640
Let's meet again

23:58.600 --> 23:59.720
and have a good chat all night long.

24:08.560 --> 24:11.440
Lord Song, I guess you owe me a favor.

24:14.120 --> 24:16.800
You used me to please His Highness.

24:17.560 --> 24:18.560
I wonder who owes me.

24:21.920 --> 24:23.520
I don't think it's 20 feet.

24:30.960 --> 24:31.840
My lady.

24:31.920 --> 24:34.240
The situation in the Duke of Ying's
residence is so urgent.

24:35.160 --> 24:36.880
Why are you still
in the mood to copy the book?

24:37.840 --> 24:40.080
Haste makes waste.
We should cope with it slowly.

24:40.160 --> 24:43.400
What we need most
right now is peace of mind.

24:50.360 --> 24:51.800
A message from Mr. Zhao.

24:51.880 --> 24:53.920
Lord Song sent an emergency report
and left the palace immediately.

24:56.960 --> 25:00.360
But what if Mr. Zhao can't stop Lord Song?

25:01.320 --> 25:03.280
If Zhao Liang Bi can't stop Song Mo,

25:04.080 --> 25:05.840
all we can do is burn our boats.

25:17.000 --> 25:17.880
Rise!

25:20.280 --> 25:22.040
Lord Song, please stop!

25:24.800 --> 25:26.240
-You're Young Lady Zhao's man.
-That's right.

25:26.320 --> 25:28.120
She told me to stop you.

25:28.200 --> 25:29.360
She said that if you
return home at this juncture,

25:29.440 --> 25:30.840
you'll put yourself behind the eight ball.

25:31.720 --> 25:33.080
My mother is seriously ill at home.

25:33.160 --> 25:34.920
As her son, I must go back.

25:35.000 --> 25:36.320
-Get out of the way.
-Lord Song!

25:39.240 --> 25:40.440
I appreciate her kindness.

25:42.360 --> 25:43.400
Lord Song!

25:46.640 --> 25:48.320
FUNERAL TRIBUTE

25:48.400 --> 25:50.400
THE DUKE OF YING'S RESIDENCE

25:57.200 --> 26:00.080
Lord Song, you're finally home!

26:00.160 --> 26:01.240
The Duchess passed away the night before.

26:01.960 --> 26:04.360
We just set up the mourning hall. Lord…

26:24.760 --> 26:27.800
LONGEVITY

26:29.080 --> 26:29.920
Mo.

26:30.480 --> 26:31.720
You're finally home.

26:34.320 --> 26:35.320
ANCESTOR TABLET OF THE VIRTUOUS WIFE,
MADAM JIANG OF THE FIRST MARRIAGE

26:35.400 --> 26:36.520
Before Mother closed her eyes,

26:37.040 --> 26:38.480
she didn't even drink
the medicine I gave her.

26:39.400 --> 26:41.160
She kept calling your name.

26:45.080 --> 26:46.280
It's my fault.

26:48.440 --> 26:49.600
I came back late.

26:53.560 --> 26:54.400
Mother.

26:55.640 --> 26:56.680
I'm home.

26:57.840 --> 26:58.720
I am unfilial.

27:00.960 --> 27:03.080
I am unfilial.

27:20.320 --> 27:21.600
Lord Song.

27:21.680 --> 27:25.080
The Duke has been heartbroken these days.

27:25.160 --> 27:26.600
He's eager to see you.

27:27.800 --> 27:28.800
Mother.

27:30.440 --> 27:31.760
I'll be right back.

27:34.120 --> 27:37.920
ANCESTOR TABLET OF THE VIRTUOUS WIFE,
MADAM JIANG OF THE FIRST MARRIAGE

27:50.560 --> 27:51.400
Your Grace.

27:52.080 --> 27:53.240
Father.

27:54.440 --> 27:56.200
Looking at this comb

27:57.120 --> 27:59.360
makes me feel like Hui Sun is still here.

27:59.960 --> 28:02.840
She just went to admire the flowers.

28:03.840 --> 28:06.840
She'll be back soon.

28:10.040 --> 28:12.080
Father, I'm unfilial.

28:14.640 --> 28:16.400
I couldn't see Mother for the last time.

28:26.120 --> 28:29.320
There's something here. Take a look.

28:30.360 --> 28:31.760
Do you recognize it?

28:37.400 --> 28:38.240
Yes, I recognize it.

28:38.920 --> 28:40.880
This is Grandfather's nephrite jade.

28:40.960 --> 28:42.360
One was given to me,

28:42.960 --> 28:44.280
while another was given to Han.

28:44.880 --> 28:46.280
I didn't bring it with me.

28:48.000 --> 28:49.240
haven't seen it for a long time.

28:50.320 --> 28:51.880
I'm glad you recognize it.

28:55.040 --> 28:59.440
The jade was found on Mei Rui.

29:01.160 --> 29:02.320
Mei Rui?

29:04.760 --> 29:06.080
Shoulder width, one and a half feet.

29:06.760 --> 29:08.560
The maid who served Mother?

29:09.600 --> 29:10.640
How did she get it?

29:11.920 --> 29:13.240
How did she get it?

29:13.960 --> 29:17.680
Why don't you ask her?

29:18.800 --> 29:19.640
Servant!

29:32.960 --> 29:33.960
How did this happen?

29:34.640 --> 29:37.040
Lord Song, just admit it.

29:37.120 --> 29:40.520
Someone saw you having
an affair with Mei Rui a long time ago.

29:41.080 --> 29:44.600
The jade pendant
must be your token of love.

29:47.040 --> 29:47.880
Father.

29:48.400 --> 29:49.240
I didn't do that!

29:49.320 --> 29:52.520
When the Duchess died,
the maid committed suicide.

29:53.280 --> 29:55.400
We thought she committed suicide
because of the Duchess.

29:55.960 --> 29:57.120
But when the physician checked her,

29:57.760 --> 29:59.920
she was already three months pregnant.

30:00.960 --> 30:03.200
When she died,

30:03.760 --> 30:05.360
she was holding this jade pendant.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.920
When you returned
to the capital three months ago,

30:08.520 --> 30:10.320
I didn't see you at all.

30:11.040 --> 30:14.680
I thought
you were busy with your uncle's matter.

30:15.400 --> 30:19.760
I didn't expect you
to do such a despicable thing!

30:21.320 --> 30:22.920
Father, I didn't do that.

30:23.000 --> 30:24.640
Lu Zheng has been
staying in the residence.

30:25.640 --> 30:26.800
He can clarify it for me.

30:27.400 --> 30:28.480
Besides,

30:28.560 --> 30:30.240
there are other maids and nannies.

30:30.320 --> 30:32.080
-I can confront them.
-You unworthy descendant!

30:32.680 --> 30:35.560
You committed adultery
when your mother was seriously ill.

30:35.640 --> 30:37.520
Are you not ashamed to make excuses?

30:37.600 --> 30:40.520
Lu Zheng has been with you for ten years.

30:40.600 --> 30:42.080
He will definitely speak for you!

30:42.160 --> 30:44.280
And the servants too!

30:44.360 --> 30:46.680
If your mother knows about this,

30:46.760 --> 30:48.960
she will be heartbroken.

30:49.720 --> 30:50.560
Father.

30:51.080 --> 30:52.240
Father, trust me.

30:52.320 --> 30:53.240
I didn't do that.

30:53.320 --> 30:54.280
That's not true!

30:54.360 --> 30:58.600
I'm going to teach you a lesson
for your mother!

31:00.800 --> 31:01.880
Father…

31:02.560 --> 31:03.600
I…

31:03.680 --> 31:04.720
Your Grace…

31:04.800 --> 31:05.960
Lord Song.

31:06.040 --> 31:08.640
The Duke is mad
because he thinks highly of you.

31:08.720 --> 31:10.080
Stop talking back.

31:10.160 --> 31:12.400
Let the Duke vent his anger first
before you explain.

31:12.480 --> 31:14.200
Stop talking to him. Servants!

31:14.280 --> 31:15.680
Drag this traitor out

31:15.760 --> 31:17.320
and punish him following the family rules!

31:26.680 --> 31:27.920
-How's it going?
-Mr. Zhao failed to stop him.

31:28.000 --> 31:29.120
Mr. Zhao failed to stop him…

31:30.800 --> 31:32.960
-Is the door of the residence closed?
-Yes.

31:35.640 --> 31:38.600
Why would they close the door after
welcoming guests to express condolences?

31:39.240 --> 31:40.120
Something's wrong.

31:40.200 --> 31:41.720
My lady, you're still grounded.

31:41.800 --> 31:44.880
If that's the case,
should we still be involved in this?

31:44.960 --> 31:47.320
We've done our best
by stopping his return home.

31:48.040 --> 31:48.880
No.

31:49.880 --> 31:50.880
I want to save him.

31:52.440 --> 31:54.160
Tell Mr. Chen to make the last move.

32:08.600 --> 32:09.560
I beg you, Grand General.

32:09.640 --> 32:12.240
Let me take responsibility for my father!

32:12.320 --> 32:13.680
I will not violate military law.

32:13.760 --> 32:15.200
I will be loyal!

32:15.880 --> 32:17.280
Everyone in the court knows that

32:17.360 --> 32:19.000
as your father,

32:19.080 --> 32:22.360
I rely on you
and Jiang Mei Sun.

32:23.240 --> 32:25.040
In His Majesty's imperial edict,

32:25.120 --> 32:27.360
he praised you as having
the character of Jiang Mei Sun.

32:27.440 --> 32:29.000
Whose son are you?

32:38.400 --> 32:40.960
RIGHTEOUS AND NOBLE SPIRIT

32:43.880 --> 32:46.440
The body is gifted by the parents.

32:47.680 --> 32:50.680
Take it if you want it.

32:51.560 --> 32:53.520
If you do not want to see me,

32:55.320 --> 32:58.040
I will never return to the capital.

32:59.960 --> 33:02.040
I will never return home.

33:03.360 --> 33:05.040
But at least tell me this.

33:06.520 --> 33:08.760
Why did you do this to me?

33:09.920 --> 33:11.400
Why?

33:13.440 --> 33:15.840
Why?

33:30.360 --> 33:31.520
Lock him up.

33:32.200 --> 33:33.960
Song Mo committed misconduct.

33:34.040 --> 33:34.920
This is intolerable.

33:35.680 --> 33:38.320
Tell my eldest brother and
Third Brother to come tomorrow.

33:38.880 --> 33:40.200
I'll remove his name from the family tree

33:40.800 --> 33:42.160
and report this to His Majesty

33:43.160 --> 33:46.560
so that His Majesty
will depose Song Mo as my successor.

34:30.080 --> 34:31.679
If your relatives are still alive,

34:31.760 --> 34:33.760
why don't you lower
your head and give it a try?

34:33.840 --> 34:35.639
It's just like wearing colorful clothes
to entertain relatives.

34:47.480 --> 34:49.159
I see…

34:55.040 --> 34:56.920
I see.

35:17.880 --> 35:18.920
Mother…

35:33.440 --> 35:34.360
Go.

36:28.200 --> 36:29.120
Lord Song.

36:30.160 --> 36:31.000
You're awake.

36:35.440 --> 36:37.120
Lord Song is awake.

36:37.800 --> 36:39.600
That's great…

36:39.680 --> 36:41.440
I'll do the remaining stuff.

36:44.840 --> 36:45.680
Lord Song.

36:50.560 --> 36:51.400
Young Lady Zhao.

36:53.120 --> 36:54.200
Where's this?

36:56.360 --> 36:57.920
Zhaowen Bookstore.

36:58.000 --> 37:00.280
Fortunately, you detained Mr. Chen.

37:00.360 --> 37:03.120
Otherwise, I wouldn't be able
to save you by myself.

37:05.640 --> 37:08.720
Your master will die soon.

37:10.400 --> 37:13.560
He'll be removed from
the family tree tomorrow.

37:14.200 --> 37:16.000
You better understand the situation now.

37:16.520 --> 37:18.720
I've prepared
the statement of confession for you.

37:19.440 --> 37:21.040
You just need to
put your fingerprint on it.

37:22.960 --> 37:24.200
Can you write?

37:24.840 --> 37:26.200
You blockhead.

37:31.320 --> 37:33.320
"Lure them away. Make a mess to save him."

37:33.400 --> 37:35.600
"Meet at the corner of the gate.
Find ways to escape."

37:37.120 --> 37:38.640
How about you come first?

37:41.560 --> 37:42.640
Don't move!

37:43.400 --> 37:45.120
Since the Duke of Ying wants us dead,

37:45.720 --> 37:47.680
I'll take all of you together!

37:50.640 --> 37:51.640
Hurry up!

37:52.520 --> 37:54.000
This way! Go now!

37:55.640 --> 37:57.880
-Hurry!
-Lord Song has run away!

37:57.960 --> 37:59.680
This way! Catch them!

38:04.880 --> 38:05.920
-Go!
-Lu Ming!

38:06.000 --> 38:07.640
-Go!
-Go now!

38:25.560 --> 38:26.800
Lu Zheng!

38:26.880 --> 38:29.600
Go! Lu Ming, go now!

38:29.680 --> 38:30.720
Lu Zheng!

38:32.400 --> 38:34.120
Take good care of Lord Song!

38:39.000 --> 38:42.240
-Lu Zheng!
-Go now! Hurry!

38:45.000 --> 38:46.440
LURE THEM AWAY. MAKE A MESS TO SAVE HIM.

38:48.000 --> 38:50.720
The father and son who sit together,
don't understand each other.

38:51.840 --> 38:53.880
But someone who is neither
a relative nor an acquaintance

38:53.960 --> 38:55.240
risked her life to save me.

38:58.280 --> 39:01.480
You left the house in the middle of
the night to meet with a male outsider.

39:01.560 --> 39:04.800
If your stepmother and
fifth uncle knew about this,

39:05.520 --> 39:06.600
do you know the consequences?

39:06.680 --> 39:07.960
This is urgent.

39:09.400 --> 39:10.800
Since I wanted to save you,

39:10.880 --> 39:12.440
I would have found a way to deal with it.

39:14.360 --> 39:17.840
What's more, you saved me before.

39:21.440 --> 39:22.600
Did I save you before?

39:25.240 --> 39:26.600
I mean

39:26.680 --> 39:29.280
you saved me before
when we were in Futing.

39:30.400 --> 39:33.440
Now that Mr. Chen has returned,
our debt is over.

39:44.080 --> 39:47.640
Your handwriting
is not as crooked as before.

39:48.760 --> 39:50.720
It seems familiar to me.

39:52.640 --> 39:55.720
IF YOUR LOVED ONES ARE STILL HERE
WHY NOT TRY HUMBLING YOURSELF?

40:02.760 --> 40:04.160
You dare not look at me.

40:05.200 --> 40:06.880
Young Lady Zhao, do you still remember?

40:07.920 --> 40:09.280
During the Granary Festival,

40:10.440 --> 40:12.880
at Guanghe Restaurant,
"The Tale of the Silken Robe"…

40:19.880 --> 40:21.240
You've got the wrong person.

40:22.200 --> 40:23.680
I don't like to watch performances.

40:28.920 --> 40:31.200
You're seriously injured.
Stop imagining things.

40:32.200 --> 40:33.640
I'll apply medicine again.

40:49.440 --> 40:50.480
Gray hair…

40:53.040 --> 40:54.080
It's her.

40:55.320 --> 40:56.920
It's her all along.

40:58.320 --> 41:00.560
She took the risk to save me
but refused to acknowledge it.

41:01.400 --> 41:03.040
Why is she avoiding me?

41:03.920 --> 41:05.520
What secret is she hiding in her heart?

41:09.120 --> 41:10.440
Your blood has turned purple.

41:10.520 --> 41:12.320
They were trying to kill me.

41:13.760 --> 41:15.000
My internal organs were hurt.

41:16.240 --> 41:17.600
So of course, the blood looks darker.

41:22.000 --> 41:23.160
What time is it now?

41:23.680 --> 41:24.560
It's 1 a.m.

41:25.520 --> 41:26.960
I was unconscious for six hours.

41:27.760 --> 41:29.480
I thought you would never wake up again.

41:31.440 --> 41:32.360
I must go back.

41:32.440 --> 41:34.200
How can you go back
when you're heavily injured?

41:34.280 --> 41:36.800
They're going to remove
my name from the family tree.

41:36.880 --> 41:38.800
The clan lineage is the most important.

41:38.880 --> 41:40.640
His Majesty will depose my position
as the Duke of Ying's son.

41:41.760 --> 41:43.120
Now that I'm in a deadlock,

41:43.880 --> 41:45.280
I'd rather move forward

41:46.440 --> 41:47.440
than stop at this juncture.

41:47.520 --> 41:49.280
But you're heavily injured.

41:49.360 --> 41:50.640
You should rest for at least a month.

41:51.480 --> 41:52.720
I can't wait.

41:53.800 --> 41:55.840
The lives of my guards are at stake

41:55.920 --> 41:57.880
and my mother just passed away.

41:59.800 --> 42:03.400
What I need now
is not recuperation.

42:07.560 --> 42:08.960
I need to be able to hold a sword.

42:10.760 --> 42:15.000
DUKE OF YING'S RESIDENCE

42:43.040 --> 42:44.840
Young Lady Zhao was punished

42:44.920 --> 42:46.160
by Mr. Dou Shi Shu under the family rules
because she went out to meet a man.

42:46.240 --> 42:48.280
-It's me.
-Lord Song!

42:49.160 --> 42:50.200
Young Lady Zhao!

42:50.280 --> 42:51.720
It was me who was bold and reckless.

42:51.800 --> 42:53.520
It was also me who was immoral.

42:53.600 --> 42:55.160
It has nothing to do with Young Lady Zhao.

42:55.240 --> 42:58.520
Mr. Dou, please punish me.

44:48.160 --> 44:50.840
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM.
